data.description: View the charm of this 4-bed, 2.5-bath two-story home in Amhurst! Embrace the open floor plan and elegant wood tile flooring downstairs, complemented by a granite kitchen top. Two dining rooms, one adorned with a captivating accent wall, provide versatile spaces. Upstairs, a delightful game room awaits. Step outside to the covered patio in the backyard - the perfect setting for family gatherings. Welcome to your new home!
